{"tid":774705,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"酒樓大廚大鬧員工：你班閪佬含家鏟連個火都未識睇啊！","createTime":"2018-08-10T13:53:40.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-10T13:58:38.000Z","uid":20430,"like":1,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"08ff5e2acd4c718c9ccd2ff97de45e74f9fc6572","tid":774705,"uid":20430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-10T13:53:40.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/groups/295202647488775/permalink/1503263880015973/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fgroups%2F295202647488775%2Fpermalink%2F1503263880015973%2F&d=E0p321MZ84jFeSRkm7K84cKJ7zzy8RXHrd%2FDXtMH0Y8%3D&h=0593d02d\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/groups/295202647488775/permalink/1503263880015973/</a><br />\n<br />\nFacebook上傳一單酒樓大廚粗口大罵員工，基本就啫啫煲重水流流、火喉力度、兜乾身等問題責罵員工。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/10/213933_26bcc3182b139f91aff7328987c3a23e.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F10%2F213933_26bcc3182b139f91aff7328987c3a23e.png&h=70b055f0&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/10/213934_e8c8fe08c1774dea5f88389159c17ed6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F10%2F213934_e8c8fe08c1774dea5f88389159c17ed6.png&h=f726fa0f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n就信息表示，該酒家為廣州羊城酒家。另外信息更講到，呢種人放工一定俾人打<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我就覺得，個大廚鬧得好，你留意返佢指責地方，佢都因認員工做錯地方講同做返出黎教，咁如果真係有做錯，呢位大廚出聲係好應該。<br />\n<br />\n用幾大火、燒煲位置如何、甚至大廚片段自己再加水去燒，佢都無煲燶同依然成煲水汪汪情況。<br />\n<br />\n如果佢真係無心話無心教，都唔會逐每一點錯誤屌人。<br />\n<br />\n另外，佢職位係大廚，咁佢有責任管理一間酒樓品質去保持口碑。所以，萬一如果有員工做到錯曬，咁真係要出聲管理。<br />\n<br />\n真係無鬧而鬧重咁好心機煮埋俾你睇咩，自己落場去跑下馬睇下股票唔好？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ff512ea6590a7d43ce010711e571c61d36fd391","tid":774705,"uid":77569,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-0